# Purchased (Envato/3DOcean) 3D asset — its licence forbids redistributing the
# raw model in this public repo. It is present locally and in private builds;
# regenerate it from your purchased OBJ with:
#   node tools/build-london-bus.mjs <path-to/LowPoly-LondonBus_OBJ.obj>
# When absent, the game falls back to the procedural double-decker automatically.
/public/models/vehicles/london-double-decker.glb
